Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:22.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}魔法の言葉 覚えている 虹の始まったところ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:30.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}あの時世界の全てに 一瞬で色が付い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:37.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}本当の声はいつだって 正しい道を照らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:45.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}なんだって疑っているから とても強く信じている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:52.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心臓が動いている事の 吸って吐いてが続く事の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:59.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心がずっと熱い事の 確かな理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:06.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}雲の向こうの銀河のように どっかで無くした切符のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:14.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}生まれる前の歴史のように 君が持っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}それだけ わかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:28.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}僕だけ わかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:22.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}記得魔法的話語 彩虹開始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:30.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}那時世界的一切 瞬間帶上了色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:37.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}真正的聲音無論何時 都在指引正確的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:45.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}無論何事都要懷疑 所以才堅定的相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:52.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心臟在搏動 呼吸在持續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:59.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}內心總是如此熾熱的 確切的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:06.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}如同雲之彼端的銀河 如同丟失在某處的車票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:14.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}如同降生前的歷史 由你持有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}只有此事 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:28.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}只有我 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}その声は流れ星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}次々に耳に 飛び込んでは光って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}魚のように集まりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}冷たかった胸に 陽だまりが出来た
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}普通の触れ方を知らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}戸惑っていたら 触れてくれた手に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:38.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}どれだけ夜をくぐり抜けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}ずっと冷めないままの熱が 脈を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}君がいるそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:54.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}命の全部が輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}凍りついた心に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:03.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}その鼓動が響き火を燈す
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}いくつもなくなったあとに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:13.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}強く残った ひとつ残った
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:18.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}離れない いつでも側に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:26.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕の中に 一番近くに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那個聲音像流星一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}接二連三的躍入耳裡 熠熠生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}像魚一樣開始聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}冰冷的胸間有了陽光的暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)\fn方正中倩繁体}因为不知道普通的接触方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}所以迷惘 對於碰觸我的那隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:38.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}無論穿越多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}一直不曾冷{\fn方正中倩繁体}却{\fn}的熱量 在鼓動著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}只因{\fn方正中倩繁体}为有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:54.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}生命的一切都綻放光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在冰凍的心間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:03.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那份鼓動迴響著 點燃火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}失去太多太多之後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:13.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}頑{\fn方正中倩繁体}强的留下 唯一留下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:18.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}不會分離 無論何時都在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:26.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在我心裡 最{\fn方正中倩繁体}为接近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(192,294)\fad(1500,0)}過去的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我完成了年內所有比賽之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得了重感冒 一直在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自蜷縮在昏暗的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎來了12月31號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口好渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃點什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有藥…得快點吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只剩最後一片藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須去買 但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 還是再睡一覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下次醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現感冒已經如謊言般退去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家閉門不出的這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因發熱變得意識模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了許多次同一個夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我小時候反覆見過的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個乘坐很長很長的手扶梯的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非對什麼感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是上升 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上升的頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有回去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別按了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 起不來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 果然感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 突入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 是小零的家欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 確保枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 拿好手機錢包鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣穿著睡衣也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加件外套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把圍巾圍好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經為你叫好計程車了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計程車？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然問要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是去看醫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是流感的話就要隔離看顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是普通的感冒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就帶你來我家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不是流感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為家裡有老人幼兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須得特別注意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃蛋花粥吧 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看過你的廚房了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都沒有吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醃梅乾可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加點進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒覺得胃口不好的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加點梅乾會清爽些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 稍微把脖子伸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用毛巾圍住脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流汗的話再換一條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為吃蛋花粥容易流汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須多流些汗來退燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾還有很多 隨時可以換哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你擦擦額頭的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那個是零的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 吃了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼喝點茶就躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打個電話回老家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一定很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已經獨立了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑 沒有什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑 蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨立呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借一下你的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手機差不多關機3天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓周圍的人這麼擔心你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能稱作是獨立哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 我是零
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零嗎 是零嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話一直打不通 我打算過去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透過電話聽到父親聲音的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才知道了自己的膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親的聲音 是真的在擔心的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 結果還是只考慮著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山 身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃個飯 再吃一次藥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻衣子出場的話叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石川小百合出場了再叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了吃晚餐的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我起床喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前還更誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比現在還多三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擠在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 感覺都要缺氧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們的父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都看著他們的睡臉抱怨著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 外婆和我三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邊收拾著邊看「過去一年將來一年」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有什麼緣由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都對父親的事絕口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 零也吃一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你睡的很香 就沒有叫你起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得把梅乾弄碎加進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便因為發燒沒味道道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道也會覺得清爽些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些我剛剛說過了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是我每次感冒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽就會說給我聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 果然會說一樣的話吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要聽見這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊覺得「又在說同樣的話了」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻又感到了安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像魔法一樣呢 媽媽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃她沒有什麼機會聽到媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大晦日這麼重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不是家人 卻還來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還讓你們費神照顧我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我希望你來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到幫助的人是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是孤獨一人 收拾著這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許會哭出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼哭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 連我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊吸著鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人一邊慌張地尋找面紙時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視裡傳來了大晦日的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣難堪地 今年在夜空中遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿心只想著自己孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒注意到其他人也是孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此愚蠢的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大晦日的鐘聲 深沉厚重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷如一條緩慢的深河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(176,294)}將來一年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1108,702)}過往一年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的一年終將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰在媽媽的衣櫃上亂貼貼紙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這個很難撕下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 能起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐說要吃早餐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還發燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退了一大半了 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙上好多廣告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小桃 這樣我都沒辦法看報紙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山要吃年糕嗎 要什麼味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要砂糖醬油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃要起司的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要起司的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們繼續吧 有請下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 還是有一點燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 總而言之先吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再吃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快進被爐裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只穿睡衣的話腳會很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是郵差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦 賀年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的 姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的 爺爺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有給小桃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 吶 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 收到很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多吶 不知道賀年狀抽獎會不會中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃也有收到了吶 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}幼稚園和小兒科醫生寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 零家說不定也有收到了呀 賀年狀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 我覺得應該沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去幫你拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.27,Top,,0,0,0,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.19,Top,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.69,Top,,0,0,0,,只會讓某些事情完全暴露出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等哦 我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑰匙借我喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:15.17,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}不忍直視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有收到啊 賀年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩…兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有收到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為不會有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一張是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龍貓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這別墅是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱氣球？CG合成的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.22,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}桐山！！期待與你C1戰之日的到來！！二海堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那另外一張是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}由衷祝賀新春\N雨傘旗魚 180CM\NPE線3號 200cm\N前導線 80磅\N於馬來西亞海上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本將棋聯盟會長 第十六代名人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神宮寺崇德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將棋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.73,Top,,0,0,0,,雨傘旗魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊？這位…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.36,Top,,0,0,0,,馬來西亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.86,Top,,0,0,0,,釣魚的老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先說清楚 這個人很強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然從以前開始就有點怪怪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是這副德行但卻當了七代名人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼要幫他辯護啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂 美咲阿姨來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是老家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆家那邊會讓人覺得肩膀發酸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.14,Top,,0,0,0,,美咲阿姨你看桃子的賀年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.52,Top,,0,0,0,,阿姨 請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你總是裝乖巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.98,Top,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 日向真是貼心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從以前開始 就只有在外面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有紅包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 日向 桃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…來 順便給你一份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將棋少年 雖然只有一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你從大晦日那天開始就感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被明里綁架過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我也有？這怎麼能收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 雖然有一陣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是跟一砂先生和史密斯先生一起來光顧過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後也拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 媽媽 美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲來拜訪你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年還打算讓明里去你那工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再讓親人幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇個新人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可從來沒有贊成過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓明里再做什麼危險的工作吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我的店一點也不危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然店面很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我高貴城堡裡都是優雅的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓明里因為家務和照顧孩子閉門不出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後漸漸變老嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子個性認真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的會扮演起母親的角色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一週兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕強迫也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必須化化妝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上漂亮衣服出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是難得的美人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人卻日漸憔悴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯過了嫁人的時機怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人能碰明里一根手指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 準確說是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不讓他們碰到的前提下狠賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把男人那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為無法觸碰而變得躁動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始花錢大手大腳的習性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢牢抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆 你的女兒是惡鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生了個惡鬼的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 吃晚餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要試試我跟小日向的力作？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我老公去看足球比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是用心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然做了年菜吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是現在比較流行的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我跟小日向一起想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面都是經過深思熟慮後選的吉祥菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是做出來很美味可口的年菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是買整條的紅白魚糕的話一定吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們就改買紅宮魚肉山芋丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用竹籤串起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出來像是糰子串一樣的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求能過上踏實的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了豌豆豬肉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求來年財運
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了金色的栗金團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求未來有更好展望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了蓮藕炒牛蒡絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求根基紮實代代相傳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就做了包牛蒡肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望外公能長壽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了烏龜狀的迷你漢堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然還有伊達卷和雙色甜蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我還試著把法蘭克福香腸做成鯛魚狀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:04.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}只負責吃的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個真是太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前美香子跟外婆也是兩人努力做出整桌年菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加些義大利麵進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要口香糖 口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年菜原來是這樣吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還帶著願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只要看見這個餐盒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會產生必須要裝滿它的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝滿餐盒後的成就感真是讓人欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這種感覺真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成就感可是每天生活中非常重要的動力來源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我能理解 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是成就感跟麻煩總是一同岀現的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也正是跨過了困難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能獲得成就感吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見呢 多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還會再來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也請多多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 能替我帶小桃去洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盤子姐姐來洗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要用到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以麻煩你先去二樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 想必你也是第一次看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實川本家的浴室就在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.59,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}在打開客廳的落地窗之後\N突然就出現了浴室！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.59,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}而且還沒有更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前家裡沒有浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直都是去澡堂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過後來家人多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就在院子裡增加了這個浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實也很希望能夠有一間更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會沒有院子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還要花很多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是每次有客人來就會覺得很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起呢 小零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零不許看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚…晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇…嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是驚人的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 藥也吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這根繩子還真是方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我可以在才認識不久的人家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣平常地睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這裡 為什麼會這麼安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會有那樣懷念的夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.53,0:22:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣吶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼回事吶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座古老的房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把時間 大家和一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至連我在內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜靜地包圍起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催人熟睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 我落入沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是已經忘了多久不曾有過的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉 柔和的沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:22:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1108,706)}將來一年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 去得到它吧 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常清楚這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.64,0:24:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下還能剩下幾天的伙食費
